body_html:
Yes, MaxPoolV2 should be hidden.

The automatically generated python doesn't seem to be exposed to the API, so it appears everything is in order. I suspect that in order to expose it it needs to be added to _allowed_symbols somewhere.

Once three weeks have passed, we need to add the wrapper which runs MaxPoolV2 whenever tf.max_pool is called.

body:
Yes, MaxPoolV2 should be hidden. 

The automatically generated python doesn't seem to be exposed to the API, so it appears everything is in order. I suspect that in order to expose it it needs to be added to _allowed_symbols somewhere.

Once three weeks have passed, we need to add the wrapper which runs MaxPoolV2 whenever tf.max_pool is called.
